description: Boston's LEED Gold certified Macallen building boasts incredible luxury units, including this oversized one bedroom with stunning views of the city's horizon. Highlights include custom cabinets, bamboo flooring, an Italian porcelain kitchen backsplash, custom lighting in every room, designer blinds, built-in living room bookshelves, and a heated attached garage parking space. Storage abounds with two designer closets in the bedroom and a custom closet in the bathroom. The Court Square Press complex includes an around the clock concierge, media room, newly refurbished gym, a luxurious heated lap pool, and grills within an oversized rooftop oasis.  This building is within close proximity to the new Ink Block; including a Whole Foods and several new restaurants.
